### =============================================================================
### RESQID — School Admin Dashboard API Tests
### File: dashboard.http
### Use with: VS Code REST Client extension  /  JetBrains HTTP Client
### =============================================================================
### SETUP:
###   1. Copy the correct value for @baseUrl below
###   2. Get a valid JWT by hitting the login endpoint first (see Auth section)
###   3. Paste the token into @authToken
###   4. Paste a real schoolId from your DB into @schoolId
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl     = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken   = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..SWbcW-xWxcDiqejOu7cL6yVRbMv7tp46d9zUO2yoecU
@schoolId    = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a7b	
@badUUID     = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a8b
@otherSchoolId = 00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000

# ── Quick login helper (get a token first) ─────────────────────────────────────
# POST {{baseUrl}}/school/auth/login
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "email": "admin@yourschool.com",
#   "password": "yourpassword"
# }

###

### =============================================================================
### ✅ HAPPY PATH
### =============================================================================

### [1] Valid request — should return full dashboard payload
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{schoolId}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ VALIDATION ERRORS — rejected at middleware, never hits DB
### =============================================================================

### [2] Missing auth token — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{schoolId}}/dashboard
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Malformed JWT — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{schoolId}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer thisisnotavalidjwt
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] schoolId is not a valid UUID — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{badUUID}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] schoolId is a UUID but belongs to a different school — expect 403 FORBIDDEN
### (JWT is valid, but tenant mismatch — school user accessing another school)
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{otherSchoolId}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] schoolId is empty string — expect 404 (route won't match)
GET {{baseUrl}}/school//dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### 🔁 CACHE BEHAVIOUR — run these in sequence to verify Redis TTL
### =============================================================================

### [7] First hit — cache MISS → DB queries run → response cached
###     Check server logs: should see Prisma query logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{schoolId}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [8] Second hit immediately after — cache HIT → no DB queries
###     Response should be identical and faster (check response time)
###     Check server logs: NO Prisma query logs this time
GET {{baseUrl}}/school/{{schoolId}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
